'''''Star Wars: The Official Magazine'' 21''' was the twenty-first issue of the ''[[Star Wars: The Official Magazine]]'', published for [[July]]/[[August]] [[1999]]. Like the previous issue, it had two covers, alternating between [[Obi-Wan Kenobi/Legends|Obi-Wan]] and [[Darth Maul/Legends|Darth Maul]].

